{
  "text": "We shall now (and hereafter), work with the variable \u03c6 rather than \u00b5, as defined in [CITATION_1] . This change of variables is well-defined since at this stage we have already taken care of all the eigenvalues lying outside the Kesten-McKay support, [\u22122",
